{"code":200,"data":[{"author":"小编","content":"<p>&nbsp; 夏天来了，随着酷热一同到来的还有2017年749万的毕业大军。据悉今年高校毕业人数创历史最高，加上历年未就业的毕业生，预计今年高校就业人数将突破800万人。然而企业针对应届毕业生的用人需求不升反降，据《2016典范企业人才招聘状况报告》显示，100家典范企业计划招聘2017届本科应<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>届毕业生45577人，比2016年的招聘量减少7.3%。而作为吸纳毕业生最多的传统民营企业，在经历了2015、2016年的倒闭潮后用人需求也锐减。预计2017年将迎来历年最难的就业季。\r\n但并不是所有行业都遇冷，近年IT企业的稳步发展与上升，让这一行业的用人需求不断增加。但大学教育的知识结构难以满足企业的用人需求，于是面对就业难的现状，很多大学毕业生选择了参加IT培训这一途径。短期培训还能安排就业，是很多教育培训机构的承诺，但一些小机构往往难以兑现承诺，在这一方面作为IT培训新锐力量的翡翠教育却做得很好，翡翠教育仅仅运作了四年就融资4.1亿元，成为IT教育行业创新模式典范，并且在就业保障方面，超越了北大青鸟、达内科技这些传统教育培训机构，博得了众多学员和<\/strong><\/span>企业的双方面好评。\r\n\r\n\r\n &nbsp; 一个贯穿了整个培训期间的就业服务，不只是一个流程那么简单。翡翠教育就业保障部门负责人如是说：翡翠教育从开班典礼到就业回访，有着一整套完善的就业服务流程，让学员在学习技能的同时不断提升自身的职业素养，从而更好的契合企业需求，增强就业竞争力。\r\n\r\n\r\n &nbsp; 翡翠教育特有的“技能+就业+创业”三位一体的保障模式，在学习技能的过程中，增加了就业和创业课程，通过职业素养课、简历制作课、面试技巧课、模拟面试实战课、优秀学员返校座谈会等课程进行就业能力的强化。<\/p>","description":"翡翠教育特有的“技能+就业+创业”三位一体的保障模式，在学习技能的过程中，增加了就业和创业课程，通过职业素养课、简历制作课、面试技巧课、模拟面试实战课、优秀学员返校座谈会等课程进行就业能力的强化。","id":3,"img":"201708/c77bff99-06eb-4727-b58c-914ec71983b3.png","imgMobile":"201708/4556aca2-4577-4ddf-8878-3330f5b0afd7.png","isDeleted":0,"keywords":"翡翠教育,就业,翡翠教育南京","publishTime":{"date":19,"day":3,"hours":0,"minutes":0,"month":6,"seconds":0,"time":1500393600000,"timezoneOffset":-480,"year":117},"resource":"翡翠教育","schoolID":6,"sequence":3,"title":"翡翠教育如何保障学员就业无忧？","type":"新闻"},{"author":"乐视","content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>这是标题<\/strong><\/p><p><strong><br/><\/strong><\/p><p><img src=\"/feicuiwb/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170724/1500861698360025828.png\" title=\"1500861698360025828.png\" alt=\"banner1.png\"/><\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">式入主。但备受外界关注的贾跃亭的行踪，却一直是个迷。<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　日前，有媒体报道称，7月22日贾跃亭已经偷偷从美国回来，引发市场关注。<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　当天，有消息称，一名接近乐视系高层的人士处证实，乐视控股创始人、董事长贾跃亭目前已经回国。一时间，关于贾跃亭是否已回国消息，引起业界猜测。<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　不过，多位守在位于北京朝阳区东四环的乐视总部乐视大厦的向乐视讨债的供应商，均向《证券日报》记者表示，他们轮流看守，这几天都没有看到贾跃亭出现在乐视大厦。<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　记者获悉，在贾跃亭被传已登机回京的两天内，有媒体人士前往北京首都机场，对每班从美国飞回北京的航班进行调查，并对航班旅客人员进行查询，发现贾跃亭的名字并未在旅客名单之列。同时，多位人士前往机场进行围堵，均未发现贾跃亭的身影。<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　7月22日，再有消息传出称贾跃亭尚未回国。其被身边人士证实，目前仍在美国，之所以没有回来，因为手头还有一些事务没有处理完，但是距离回国不会太久。<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　对此，一位乐视方面表示：“贾跃亭确实没有回过乐视大厦。”至于回国的具体时间，他表示：“这是贾总自己安排的，我们也不能掌握。”<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　在辞去乐视网的一切职务后，贾跃亭出任乐视汽车生态全球董事长。在贾跃亭身居美国期间，其加速了对汽车产业新战略的实施，同时尽一切所能尽快推进FF91量产。<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　虽然贾跃亭回国时间还不能确定，但讨债者们，仍在乐视大厦总部等着他。<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　就在乐视网召开第三届董事会选举新一任董事长当天，乐视大厦门口的地上还躺了二十多名讨债者。他们对贾跃亭回国一事保持高度关注，并一直询问着记者：“有没有贾跃亭的最新消息？”<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　记者了解到，苦等乐视和贾跃亭数十天后，由于讨债成本过高，他们不愿再支付住宿费，转而从网上购买了十几顶帐篷，直接在乐视大厦门口“安营扎寨”。&nbsp;<\/p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, u5FAEu8F6Fu96C5u9ED1, Arial, SimSun, u5B8Bu4F53; white-space: normal;\">　　相比乐视网新董事长是谁，贾跃亭何时回国，成为讨债者最关心的问题。<\/p><p><img src=\"http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0013.gif\"/><\/p><p><img src=\"/feicuiwb/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170726/1501039010047029941.jpg\" title=\"1501039010047029941.jpg\"/><\/p><p><img src=\"/feicuiwb/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170726/1501039010022076855.jpg\" title=\"1501039010022076855.jpg\"/><\/p><p><img src=\"/feicuiwb/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170726/1501039010035031099.jpg\" title=\"1501039010035031099.jpg\"/><\/p><p><img src=\"/feicuiwb/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170726/1501039010192037146.jpg\" title=\"1501039010192037146.jpg\"/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p>","description":"乐视集团简介","id":28,"img":"201708/dc286ee9-fe4e-471f-b06d-8bd1ba9031a0.png","imgMobile":"201708/f5b859ae-bf3c-4f8b-81d7-4161e9754ba5.png","isDeleted":0,"keywords":"乐视","publishTime":{"date":22,"day":6,"hours":0,"minutes":0,"month":6,"seconds":0,"time":1500652800000,"timezoneOffset":-480,"year":117},"resource":"雷士","schoolID":0,"sequence":3,"title":"乐视集团","type":"新闻"},{"author":"美女","content":"<p>a呼啦回复了哈防化服<br/><\/p>","description":"独立独立打了电话","id":29,"img":"201708/ea930afe-870f-4266-8d49-80ddc2d02b28.png","imgMobile":"201708/d7e68f90-8050-4aaf-a57d-315f5ce3828a.png","isDeleted":0,"keywords":"大讲的就短短几的","publishTime":{"date":11,"day":5,"hours":0,"minutes":0,"month":7,"seconds":0,"time":1502380800000,"timezoneOffset":-480,"year":117},"resource":"翡翠教育","schoolID":0,"sequence":3,"title":"移动端新闻1","type":"新闻"},{"author":"美女","content":"<p>大动画了的花了很多<\/p>","description":"大都懒得京东","id":30,"img":"201708/784faeaf-042b-4312-bf92-75d7b0e24a03.png","imgMobile":"201708/f2648930-a7bf-4d55-8b53-02cb7389c272.png","isDeleted":0,"keywords":"翰林华府,大都懒得","publishTime":{"date":11,"day":5,"hours":0,"minutes":0,"month":7,"seconds":0,"time":1502380800000,"timezoneOffset":-480,"year":117},"resource":"123","schoolID":0,"sequence":3,"title":"移动端活动1","type":"新闻"},{"author":"小编","content":"<p><strong>翡翠教育西南区-网络营销人才专场招聘会实录HR和学员一对一交流\r\n就在5月25号，成都、重庆两城联动共同开启了翡翠教育西南区网络营销人才专场招聘会。\r\n翡翠教育西南区成都分会场<\/strong><\/p>","description":"翡翠教育西南区-网络营销人才专场招聘会，两地会场共请来二十余家企业，有十六名求聘者直接被录取，还有二十多名等待到企业实地复试。","id":2,"img":"201708/b5c3fa54-1642-414a-8c2c-88824768d668.png","imgMobile":"201708/331787b8-2d84-461b-a0f2-1d6046dd5773.png","isDeleted":0,"keywords":"网络营销招聘,翡翠教育","publishTime":{"date":19,"day":3,"hours":0,"minutes":0,"month":6,"seconds":0,"time":1500393600000,"timezoneOffset":-480,"year":117},"resource":"翡翠教育","schoolID":1,"sequence":2,"title":"网络营销人才专场招聘HR和学员一对一交流","type":"新闻"},{"author":"小编","content":"<p>本次峰会首度将焦点对准有融资需求的企业与全国知名风险投资机构，为两者搭建了纯粹、平等、效率的线下再融资平台。 90位优质项目创始人与200家知名投资机构汇聚一堂。在活动现场，翡翠教育也与今年大热的IT科技、消费升级等行业的明星企业进行了沟通交流。\r\n新东方创始人俞敏洪出现在2017创新中国春季峰会上，他分享了四个观点给创业者：第一，创业本身要放松一点，游戏心态，输了再来。第二点就是少谈情怀多谈模式，坚持尝试。第三，做商业模式要独树一帜不要跟风要差异竞争。第四，主导局面，树立威望，组建强大的队伍。\r\n翡翠教育自2012年成立以来一直看好IT职业教育的未来，即便这些年北大青鸟止步了高速扩张，达内科技也开始发展非IT培训业务，翡翠教育一直坚守在IT职业教育这条赛道上。翡翠教育的坚守直到2015年终于实现了突破式的发展，用“科技+创新”逐步打开了全国的一二线市场，实现了全国直营校区70家，培养学员一万余人，实现了5亿元的营业收入。这样靓丽的经营状况很多不知情的人对此保持怀疑的态度。<\/p>","description":"翡翠教育受邀参加2017创新中国春季峰会。 本次峰会由创业邦主办，旨在为更多的创业企业、投资方建立对接模式，截至目前，已累计助力600余家企业融资超过50亿。","id":4,"img":"201708/4ee22991-25c2-45aa-a4b1-7a390d377580.png","imgMobile":"201708/2f2165ad-b1c9-422e-a77f-0b6001b98f6a.png","isDeleted":0,"keywords":"翡翠教育,苏州翡翠教育","publishTime":{"date":18,"day":2,"hours":0,"minutes":0,"month":6,"seconds":0,"time":1500307200000,"timezoneOffset":-480,"year":117},"resource":"翡翠教育","schoolID":7,"sequence":2,"title":"翡翠教育受邀参加2017创新中国春季峰会","type":"新闻"},{"author":"滴答滴答","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>库存材料还穿<\/strong><\/span>插了从<\/p><p><img src=\"/feicuiwb/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170721/1500639530199042061.jpg\" title=\"1500639530199042061.jpg\" alt=\"6ab522ef-e0c5-4fa7-92e8-c4a4063da25c.jpg\"/><\/p><p>好厉害雕梁画栋老大<\/p><p><img src=\"/feicuiwb/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170721/1500639539260095480.png\" title=\"1500639539260095480.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20170721181419.png\"/><\/p><p><br/><\/p>","description":"的好哒拉黑的","id":24,"img":"201708/6adfcbc1-09cf-43fe-823d-cd6b7c392c41.png","imgMobile":"201708/8ce99e18-7f58-4b9c-8ae1-571f7031ba80.png","isDeleted":0,"keywords":"电话卡雕梁画栋","publishTime":{"date":21,"day":5,"hours":0,"minutes":0,"month":6,"seconds":0,"time":1500566400000,"timezoneOffset":-480,"year":117},"resource":"打的看到过","schoolID":0,"sequence":2,"title":"大好哒老大","type":"新闻"},{"author":"小编","content":"<p><br/><\/p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">随着信息产业的高速发展，<\/span><\/strong><\/span><br/><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p><p>以Inter<strong>net为传播媒介的网络营销成为当今最热门的营销推广方式。与传统推广方式相比，网络营销具有得天独厚的优势，是实施现代营销媒体战略的重要一部分。而随着上网人数的迅速增加，覆盖的受众面越来越全面，网络营销的影响力也越来越大。<br/><br/><\/strong><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p><p><br/><\/p>","description":"随着信息产业的高速发展，以互联网为传播媒介的网络营销成为当今最热门的营销推广方式，是实施现代营销媒体战略的重要一部分。","id":1,"img":"201708/fd6ccd43-ddbd-4e37-9e33-59a3ea1a95e1.png","imgMobile":"201708/6a2af8e0-dc99-4dbb-88b6-d32dc2e861be.png","isDeleted":0,"keywords":"sem,seo,网络营销,电商,新媒体","publishTime":{"date":11,"day":2,"hours":0,"minutes":0,"month":6,"seconds":0,"time":1499702400000,"timezoneOffset":-480,"year":117},"resource":"翡翠教育","schoolID":1,"sequence":1,"title":"实战干货才是我们的核心竞争力wer","type":"新闻"}],"msg":"请求成功"}